{"title":"Zefal’s New Z Adventure T1 Bolt Top Tube Bag Has the Most Mounting Holes We’ve seen","link":"https://bikerumor.com/zefals-z-adventure-t1-bolt-top-tube-bag-most-mounting-holes/","date":1726840800000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Zefal-Z-Adventure-T1-and-T1-Bolt-Top-Tube-Bag-hero-jpeg.webp\" width=\"1207\" height=\"805\" alt=\"(Photos / Zefal)\" /></p>\n<p>A lot of cyclists use top tube bags for carrying some ride essentials. These could be a phone, snacks, gloves, tools, or a power bank for long rides. Zefal has introduced their latest version of a top tube bag with the <a href=\"https://www.zefal.com/en/frame-bags/695-z-adventure-t1-bolt.html\" target=\"_blank\">Z Adventure T1 and T1 Bolt,</a> a bag that uses 100% welded construction and a waterproof zip.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Zefal-Z-Adventure-T1-and-T1-Bolt-Top-Tube-Bag-side-view-jpeg-e1726686457910.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1123\" height=\"471\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Zefal-Z-Adventure-T1-and-T1-Bolt-Top-Tube-Bag-side-view-jpeg-e1726686457910.webp\" alt=\"Zefal Z Adventure T1 and T1 Bolt Top Tube Bag side view\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Zefal-Z-Adventure-T1-and-T1-Bolt-Top-Tube-Bag-side-view-jpeg-e1726686457910.webp 1123w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Zefal-Z-Adventure-T1-and-T1-Bolt-Top-Tube-Bag-side-view-jpeg-e1726686457910-297x125.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Zefal-Z-Adventure-T1-and-T1-Bolt-Top-Tube-Bag-side-view-jpeg-e1726686457910-120x50.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Zefal-Z-Adventure-T1-and-T1-Bolt-Top-Tube-Bag-side-view-jpeg-e1726686457910-768x322.webp 768w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photos / Zefal)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Z Adventure T1 is a universal top tube bag that can be mounted to any bike of your choice… road, gravel, fat, cargo, townie, or MTB. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Zefal-Z-Adventure-T1-and-T1-Bolt-Top-Tube-Bag-mesh-pocket-jpeg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"998\" height=\"682\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Zefal-Z-Adventure-T1-and-T1-Bolt-Top-Tube-Bag-mesh-pocket-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Zefal Z Adventure T1 and T1 Bolt Top Tube Bag mesh pocket\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Zefal-Z-Adventure-T1-and-T1-Bolt-Top-Tube-Bag-mesh-pocket-jpeg.webp 998w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Zefal-Z-Adventure-T1-and-T1-Bolt-Top-Tube-Bag-mesh-pocket-297x203.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Zefal-Z-Adventure-T1-and-T1-Bolt-Top-Tube-Bag-mesh-pocket-120x82.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Zefal-Z-Adventure-T1-and-T1-Bolt-Top-Tube-Bag-mesh-pocket-768x525.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Zefal-Z-Adventure-T1-and-T1-Bolt-Top-Tube-Bag-cable-port-jpeg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"732\" height=\"804\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Zefal-Z-Adventure-T1-and-T1-Bolt-Top-Tube-Bag-cable-port-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Zefal Z Adventure T1 and T1 Bolt Top Tube Bag cable port\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Zefal-Z-Adventure-T1-and-T1-Bolt-Top-Tube-Bag-cable-port-jpeg.webp 732w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Zefal-Z-Adventure-T1-and-T1-Bolt-Top-Tube-Bag-cable-port-273x300.webp 273w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Zefal-Z-Adventure-T1-and-T1-Bolt-Top-Tube-Bag-cable-port-109x120.webp 109w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>To help keep things in order inside the bag, the Z Adventure T1 is equipped with a key hook, an internal mesh pocket, and an integrated, unique cable channel. The channel is located in the center of the bag, giving the user the ability to run a USB charging cable to power or charge a light, cycling computer, or phone. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Zefal-Z-Adventure-T1-and-T1-Bolt-Top-Tube-Bag-T1-Bolt-underside-jpeg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"578\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Zefal-Z-Adventure-T1-and-T1-Bolt-Top-Tube-Bag-T1-Bolt-underside-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Zefal Z Adventure T1 and T1 Bolt Top Tube Bag T1 Bolt underside\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Zefal-Z-Adventure-T1-and-T1-Bolt-Top-Tube-Bag-T1-Bolt-underside-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Zefal-Z-Adventure-T1-and-T1-Bolt-Top-Tube-Bag-T1-Bolt-underside-297x134.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Zefal-Z-Adventure-T1-and-T1-Bolt-Top-Tube-Bag-T1-Bolt-underside-120x54.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Zefal-Z-Adventure-T1-and-T1-Bolt-Top-Tube-Bag-T1-Bolt-underside-768x347.webp 768w\" /></a><figcaption>Z Adventure T1 Bolt</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>What initially caught our attention was the bottom of the T1 Bolt which has enough holes to pass as Swiss cheese. The T1 Bolt, uses the bike’s top tube mounting points for bolting it directly to the top tube – but those mounting bolts don’t always line up with where you want to mount the bag. We’ve seen other bags with a few different mounting options, but Zefal cut to the chase lining almost the entire bottom of the bag with mounting holes. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Zefal-Z-Adventure-T1-and-T1-Bolt-Top-Tube-Bag-waterproof-jpeg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"936\" height=\"624\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Zefal-Z-Adventure-T1-and-T1-Bolt-Top-Tube-Bag-waterproof-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Zefal Z Adventure T1 and T1 Bolt Top Tube Bag waterproof\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Zefal-Z-Adventure-T1-and-T1-Bolt-Top-Tube-Bag-waterproof-jpeg.webp 936w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Zefal-Z-Adventure-T1-and-T1-Bolt-Top-Tube-Bag-waterproof-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Zefal-Z-Adventure-T1-and-T1-Bolt-Top-Tube-Bag-waterproof-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Zefal-Z-Adventure-T1-and-T1-Bolt-Top-Tube-Bag-waterproof-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Zefal-Z-Adventure-T1-and-T1-Bolt-Top-Tube-Bag-waterproof-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Zefal-Z-Adventure-T1-and-T1-Bolt-Top-Tube-Bag-waterproof-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>Z Adventure T1 &amp; T1 Bolt Specs and Retail</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Retail: $44 (T1 and T1 Bolt)</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Z Adventure T1 Specs</h3>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Type</strong>: Top-tube frame bags</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Material</strong>: Polyester 420D TPU</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Dimensions</strong> : 220 mm x 50 mm x 100 mm</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Weight</strong>: 150 g</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Mounting</strong>: Self-gripping straps</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Capacity</strong>: 1L</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Closing</strong>: Waterproof zip</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Maximum load</strong>: 1kg</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h3>Z Adventure T1 Bolt Specs</h3>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Type</strong>: Top-tube frame bags</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Material</strong>: Polyester 420D TPU</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Dimensions</strong>: 220 mm x 50 mm x 100 mm</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Weight</strong>: 150 g</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Mounting</strong>: M5 x 16mm screws (included)</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Capacity</strong>: 1L</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Closing</strong>: Waterproof zip</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Maximum load</strong>: 1kg</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.zefal.com/en/\" target=\"_blank\">Zefal.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/zefals-z-adventure-t1-bolt-top-tube-bag-most-mounting-holes/\">Zefal’s New Z Adventure T1 Bolt Top Tube Bag Has the Most Mounting Holes We’ve seen</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Ron Frazelle","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"9c2fbb8da9ddde7d7e04aac8359029ad0ab5f421bf4e5bc0e952aa18ba5dc255","category":"Cycling"}